Scenario 
---------- 

Counter-Terrorists

It is 24th December, and a group of Terrorists has taken 4 people hostage in a small Apartment complex, 
located in the Mountainside Village of Eve, Switzerland.
A counterterrorist unit has been dispatched to rescue them. 
Make your way from the churchyard deployment point through the small village to the residence, then rescue the hostages, 
rendezvouing back at the churchyard for evac.

Terrorists

You have taken 4 people hostage, and must hold them until your demands are met. 
This time of year is perfect for media attention. 
Hold the hostages against all odds. If all else fails, execute them!

This map is a little unorthodox for a CS map, since the hostages have been executed already. It is almost like an "escape" map from back in the day. The terrorists have just robbed a bank's vault, and must make their way up through either the subway or the main building to get out. This map could be considered a "Team deathmatch" as the only way I could find to win was to eliminate the opposing team. As for the layout, the counter-terrorists start on ground level in a park. The terrorists start in the vault of the bank. From the vault they can either escape through the bank or navigate through the sewer/railway system. Both escapes are tight and a good CT team can contain the terrorists from escaping. In the bank portion of the map, you will find the 4 hostages, except they are dead as I mention before. The bank has a cashier dest and a wall behind it that make great cover. There are cubicles on each side of the walls. Windows give any CT sniper a good view into the bank. The map came with no nav file, and my computer took 9 minutes to make one (which is a really long amount of time) so I provided it in the zip.

-Hello guys! We present to you our  map , based on western topic and inspired from western classic.

We hope you will enjoy. :)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Story: A filming platform has been attacked by some unknown terrorists. Bandits have demanded $ 500,000 for the release of hostages plus a helicopter.

Counter Terrorists: Our state does not fulfill the requirements of terrorists! Eliminate all  terrorists and save hostages!

Terrorists: We can expect a wave of counterattack. Under no circumstances don't let counter-terrorists to escape the hostages! They represent our guarantee of success.

Notes: Four hostages remained alive on the filming platform. Three hostages are on the roof of a house on the right of the damaged train. Another hostage is on the roof of a house on the left of the train.

Credits: 

Marin Colta - main level designer, idea of map, basic geometry & lights, positioning objects, main object and position, hostages placement.

Dmitry Ghervas - mentor, minimap, errors & bugs fixing, 3D sky, editing of bot navigation.
